here are 3 small things that instantly make a website feel more premium:

    1. lenis scroll
    2. view transitions
    3. pressed states on buttons
    everyone knows hover states. not everyone uses pressed states.
    my go-to is a simple scale(0.99) on press. tiny change, big difference. gives you that clicky ux feedback.
